# Mess Khojo - Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Build "Mess Khojo", a web application connecting users with mess/hostel rooms.
- **Admin Interface**: Secure login, manage room listings (photos, details).
- **User Interface**: Public access to view room listings.
- **Tech Stack**: React (Frontend), Node.js/Express (Backend), SQLite (Database), Local Storage for images.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> Using a local SQLite database and local file storage for simplicity and "free" usage without cloud setup. This means the app is self-contained.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend (Server)
#### [NEW] server/package.json
- Dependencies: `express`, `sqlite3`, `cors`, `multer`, `bcrypt`, `jsonwebtoken`.

#### [NEW] server/index.js
- Main server entry point.
- API Routes:
    - `POST /api/auth/login`: Admin login.
    - `GET /api/rooms`: Get all rooms (public).
    - `POST /api/rooms`: Add room (protected).
    - `DELETE /api/rooms/:id`: Delete room (protected).
    - `POST /api/upload`: Handle image uploads.

#### [NEW] server/db.js
- Database initialization (Tables: `users` (admins), `rooms`).

### Frontend (Client)
