## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- None planned for this prototype phase.

### Manual Verification
- Start backend server.
- Start frontend dev server.
- Navigate to `/admin/login`, log in with default credentials.
- Add a room with photo and details.
- Verify room appears on Admin Dashboard.
- Navigate to `/` (Home) as a user.
- Verify room appears with correct details.
